subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Ryan Moore, the 24-year-old former United States Amateur champion, matched his career low round with a seven-under-par 63 yesterday to take a three-stroke lead halfway through the Fry’s Electronics Open in Scottsdale, Ariz. Moore was at 11-under 129.
